You are solely responsible for the User Content that you make available via the Platform or otherwise. You agree that we are only acting as a passive conduit for your online distribution and publication of your User Content.
If you wish to remove your User Content from the Platform, manually delete it from the Platform. If you are having difficulties performing this, feel free to go to our Care Center or reach out to the Members Care team.
