Overview: We need to perform our services and contract with you. When you upload your Content, you grant us a license to use that content to provide our services and promote UNUM's businesses (for example, show your photos, tell your story, allow us to resize if need be for your screen size, feature you in the new features, etc.). These terms are standard by many companies (see any of your favorite or popular social media networks, software tools, social media scheduling platforms, etc.). We like to set the standard, so we went the extra mile and let you opt out of the UNUM business User License Grant clause, like member featuring, promotions, adverts, spotlights, etc. NDB. We like to think we're the unsung hero in these usually boring to read Terms and Conditions lol.
PAID SERVICES
First and foremost,
We love what we do and hope we're able to make a living out of it. All we need is to keep the lights on, allow our team to put food on the table, and be able to grow our team so we can build faster, keep ahead of competition, and bring more amazing features to you!
Our vision is to make the storytelling process easy and simple for everyone. We know not everyone has the means to contribute financially to support the UNUM fam. We understand that firsthand (we're a startup, we know how tight finances can be). We will NEVER put that burden on you. So do not feel obligated by any means if you cannot provide the finances. We do our best to support every type of storyteller and provide them with a membership plan, but let us know if we should look into other membership types (Our Members Care team are all ears)! If you believe in our team, our community, and what we are building and are able to offer financial support -- please join a membership that works for you and brings the most value to your storytelling process. Thank you in advance for your support, you will never know how much that means to our team. Together, we are what makes the UNUM story come to life.
