If you delete your User Contributions from the Platform, copies of your User Contributions may remain viewable in cached and archived pages, or might have been copied or stored by other Platform users.  Proper access and use of information provided on the Platform, including User Contributions, is governed by our terms of use at
https://www.unum.la/terms-of-service
